title: Untouchable (Taylor's Version)
description:
WHO KNEW THAT THIS SONG WAS A COVER?! Taylor Swift took a rock song and completely changed it! Lacey, Amy, Ana and Nick break down this song and take a trip down SNL memory lane!
What did we miss? What songs would you like to hear covered? Let us know!
